article_id:1644,category_name:News,title_name:Game Live Japan 2020 Dragalia Lost Livestream Gifts,image_path:,message:<div>Thank you to those who tuned in to watch the livestream of Dragalia Lost shown during the Game Live Japan 2020 event produced by Kadokawa Game Linkage, the publisher of games media such as Famitsu and Dengeki.</div><div><br></div><div>Since the Alberian Battle Royale endeavors were completed during the livestream, the following gifts have been sent to players who started playing before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601200800"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Gifts</div><div>・Sunlight Ore x5</div><div>・Summon Voucher x3</div><div><br></div><div>Note: Players can claim these gifts from their goodie boxes for up to seven days after they are received. If the gifts aren&#39;t retrieved within seven days, they will be lost.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1601200800,update_time1601199291